<p>Use Bloom's Taxonomy for formulating the learning outcomes:</p>

<table class="table table-striped table-bordered table-condensed">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Taso</th>
      <th>Määritelmä</th>
      <th>Avainsanoja</th>
